  <h2 class="text-center font-display text-[24px] leading-[112%] tracking-[-0.02em] text-ink sm:text-headline">
    <span class="sm:block">The shelf you can&rsquo;t see is </span><span class="sm:block">already shaping demand</span>
  </h2>

